PODS
---

ITS A BASIC BUILDING BLOCK ORSHEDULED UNIT,, IN EVERY POD IT HAS ONE OR MORE CONTAINRE,, MOSTLY ONE CONTAINER
WITH THE HELP OF PODS KUBERNETES DEPLOY MULTIPLE DEPENDENT CONTAINERS
KBS IRST INTERACT WITH PODS THEN IT WILL COMMUNICATE WITH CONTAINER
EVERY POD HAS ONE UNIQUE IP ADDRESS

HOW TO CHECKEISTING PODS?
KUBECTL GOT PO (OR) KUBECTL GET PODS

HOW TO CREATE A POD??
CREATE ONE YAML AND GICES THE POD DEFINATION, in kbs all thins will be done by yaml file,, 

apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: my-pod
  labels: 
    app: myapp
    

